# 🚀 ContractIQ — Enterprise Contract Lifecycle, Approval & Governance Platform

> **ContractIQ** is a production-grade backend platform for managing the full contract lifecycle — from creation and approval to activation, expiry, governance, notifications, and operational intelligence.

