# 🔄 Contract Lifecycle (Finite State Machine)

Each contract follows a controlled lifecycle:

```text
DRAFT
  ↓ Submit for Review
UNDER_REVIEW
  ↓ All approvals completed
APPROVED
  ↓ Sign
SIGNED
  ↓ Activate
ACTIVE
  ↓ Expire / Terminate
EXPIRED / TERMINATED
```

### Built With:

* Spring State Machine
* Role-based transition validation
* Audit logging for every state change

---

# 👥 Multi-Step Approval Workflow

Every contract passes through structured approval:

```text
Vendor → Legal Manager → Finance → Admin
```

## Key Features

### ✅ Sequential Approval

Each approver acts only when their step becomes active.

### ✅ Approval Rounds

Rejected contracts can be edited and re-submitted safely.

### ✅ Current Step Tracking

System always knows:

```text
Who needs to approve right now?
```

### ✅ Governance Protection

Contracts cannot bypass approval hierarchy.

