# 📜 Audit + Observability Layer

## MongoDB Notification Logs

Tracks:

* eventId
* eventVersion
* delivery status
* retry attempts
* read/unread state
* timestamps

## Contract Audit Logs

Tracks:

* actor
* role
* old status
