# 📦 Spring Batch Governance Automation

ContractIQ includes scheduled governance systems.

---

## ⏳ Contract Expiry Automation

```text
ACTIVE + endDate < today
        ↓
EXPIRED
        ↓
Audit + Notification
```

---

## 🔔 Approval Reminder Automation

```text
PENDING > 48h
      ↓
Notify current approver
```

---

## 🚨 Approval Escalation Automation

```text
PENDING > 5 days
      ↓
Escalate to Admin
```

